c: 6
v: 148
t: "Those who associate partners (with Allah) will say, \"Had Allah willed we would not have associated partners (with Allah) nor our forefathers nor we would have made anything unlawful (by ourselves).\" Thus did those before them deny, till they tasted Our punishment. Say, \"Do you have any knowledge, then bring it out for us, you follow nothing but conjecture and you do nothing but lie"